Class MergerConfig<E extends Entity>

    E - The Entitiy which can be handled by the station
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.Class<? extends E>,java.lang.Integer>

    public class MergerConfig<E extends Entity>
extends java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Class<? extends E>,java.lang.Integer>
    This class is used by the Merger construct for composing the ratio of entities needed for the merging process. The Mergerconfig is a Hashmap with key=The class of the Entity and Value= an integer of the number of required entities.
